findings.message: Long close time: Records that take longer than 7 days to go from resolved to closed
Slow resolution time: Incidents that took more than 12 hours between Work In Progress and Resolved
Misuse of On Hold state: Incidents moving to On Hold state two or more times
Process step missed: Incidents go directly to Resolved and Closed
Incident opened and resolved by the same person
Ping-Pong between In progress and On Hold
Solution rejection issue: Incident resolution rejected by custmer one or more times
